item.title: No gui in server files or clinet files
item.dc:creator: @Rene_eats_waffl3z Rene eats waffl3z
item.description:
@Rene_eats_waffl3z wrote:

If there’s no GUI.java it will load from a different class.
Right click your run file and look what main class is being executed upon run.
Then the things you would like to edit are there.
